		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Haiti Help Resources</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Update: more resources I picked up on&nbsp; a security list just now (I&#39;m drowning in email here!) Apologies for any duplication. Update 2: more additions below. @imaguid&nbsp;pointed out in a microblog that there&#39;s a pattern to the use of social engineering around disasters like the Haiti earthquake:&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;first comes the tragedy, then malware purveyors exploiting the</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2010-01-14 04:47:19">14 Jan 2010 - 04:47AM</time>
		</span>
